, ♀, 5. Posterior portion of mesosoma; 6. Mesosoma, lateral view; 7. Posterior portion of propodeum; 8. Lower lateral portion of propodeum; 9. T1, dorsal view; 10. T2, dorsal view; 11. Posterior metasomal segments, dorsal view.
